HEADWORD: Gowk
<hw>Gowk</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Gawk</er>.]</ety> <def>To make a, booby of one); to stupefy.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

