==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Gowk
<hw>Gowk</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Gawk</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The European cuckoo; -- called also
gawky.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A simpleton; a gawk or gawky.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gowl</ent>⟦br⟧
